Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.42,0:00:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.22,0:00:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.99,0:00:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What was your usual again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you remember it already, Robby?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.00,0:00:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A hamburger with extra cheese...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.70,0:00:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,lots of ketchup, and thick tomatoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.00,0:00:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you if you put pickles on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How am I supposed to remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.45,0:00:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That Chinese or Vietnamese person...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been sniffing around about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That customer has been in here a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.59,0:00:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He was asking me who you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not Chinese or Vietnamese.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.74,0:00:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of that, he's a brain surgeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.98,0:01:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,With excellent skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.25,0:01:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.71,0:01:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.20,0:01:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's the former fiancé of a\Nhospital director's daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to make Eva do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.14,0:01:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.61,0:01:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being too familiar with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.47,0:01:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How long do you plan on playing the fiancé?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.01,0:01:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.54,0:01:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,not only aren't you a doctor anymore,\Nbut you're a fugitive, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to where you belong and fix yourself up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.98,0:01:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You might be released someday,\Nif you're an exemplary inmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.06,0:01:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Release Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.16,0:01:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Release her?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not holding her or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.90,0:01:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.70,0:01:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,she's going to parties every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.37,0:01:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.24,0:01:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,See her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mess up my diner!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop hanging around here. Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.52,0:02:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.29,0:02:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.12,0:03:51.58,Title,,0,0,0,,{\be1}{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,340)}The Man Who Saw the Devil
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You met kenzo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.02,0:03:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:03:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought I should let you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,He wanted to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.31,0:04:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you didn't punch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.98,0:04:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't do something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.31,0:04:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We're leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.71,0:04:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're done with today's party?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just today's party...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The party's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice work, Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:41.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to have dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.21,0:04:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,you took her to the restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.05,0:04:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're having your dinner here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:05:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to the food served at parties\Nor high-class restaurants...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the hamburgers here are much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.09,0:05:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if that's a compliment or an insult.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.61,0:05:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You're persistent, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.94,0:05:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to get hurt again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.78,0:05:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you get it when I told you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.92,0:05:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move, Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll shoot if you do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What a dangerous doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.49,0:05:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Who hired you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.53,0:05:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you work for The Baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.77,0:05:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the one who ordered you to look after Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.34,0:05:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,was someone even higher in the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.80,0:05:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who gave you the order?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.87,0:05:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:06:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I do know his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He wears glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.81,0:06:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A man that wears glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.48,0:06:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he forcing Eva to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you already.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.95,0:06:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He's only making her appear at parties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.72,0:06:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She drinks, eats, and then goes home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.76,0:06:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva must be doing something special there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.80,0:06:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.44,0:06:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.67,0:06:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.08,0:06:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman pointed at someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Pointed at someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,At a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.42,0:06:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A young man...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.29,0:06:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,At a blond...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,young man with a pretty face.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.26,0:06:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all she did, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.26,0:06:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Eva right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,She's having dinner with my glasses-wearing boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:06:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.44,0:06:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.37,0:07:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.61,0:07:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva's job is probably over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After I've finished this job....{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.11,0:07:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll surely be killed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.22,0:07:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The party's over.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.32,0:07:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Eva?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.13,0:07:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.28,0:07:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent her back to her hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a gun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided not to carry a gun with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.07,0:08:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.14,0:08:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.71,0:08:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The party was going normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The smell of alcohol.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.12,0:08:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The fragrance of perfumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.96,0:08:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaningless laughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Except for that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva pointed at a young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the glasses guy appeared...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,bringing with him another well-dressed young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And then the two young men...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.22,0:08:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,shook hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't notice it at the time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.56,0:08:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,it appears that with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva's job was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're the one who's assigned to kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The alcohol is starting to kick in...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't have anything left.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.06,0:09:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you can't shoot me in this hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.53,0:09:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you shot your girlfriend before...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and stood in a sea of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.61,0:09:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then take me outside and shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.14,0:09:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Or else you'll have to pay for making the room all dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:10:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one thing left that I'm attached to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well. It doesn't really matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.36,0:10:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what I did today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw me pointing at someone, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.40,0:10:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably did something terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.30,0:10:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I lured someone horrible to the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I lured Mephisto and Faust together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I don't have to attend parties anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have invitations for upcoming parties here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like, after I die...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.10,0:10:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,would you fill in for me and see what I did?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.20,0:10:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.24,0:10:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,would you please finish me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:10:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's run away together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.72,0:11:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You must've gotten the wrong idea or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.52,0:11:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Run away with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.09,0:11:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.19,0:11:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Since when did we become that close?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.30,0:11:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,can't kill people anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.90,0:11:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't kill people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.14,0:11:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then can you kill devils?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.21,0:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That suit and tie I bought you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,looks exactly like what Kenzo used to wear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.28,0:11:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just dressing you up to look like Kenzo Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.43,0:11:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry up and kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.29,0:12:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I kill devils?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.17,0:12:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.80,0:12:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to sleep off this buzz a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll die if you sleep in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. Just leave me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You look grim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I always look grim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Did someone come looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, the Japanese guy from last night left this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Hellblau Hotel, room 205.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:13:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He said to contact him there if anything happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.16,0:14:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If I get full on shitty hamburgers...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll lose my will to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.27,0:14:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A party.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.50,0:14:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.34,0:14:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I can get into anywhere with just one necktie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is he a devil?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He shook so many hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that his hand should have been swollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he left the party hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sixth floor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.41,0:15:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But which room?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.79,0:15:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, have a seat here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.20,0:15:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to be modest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.57,0:15:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to see him as well, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm waiting for him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:15:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.81,0:16:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about something until he arrives.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.18,0:16:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.48,0:16:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.58,0:16:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about the world coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid kept talking like a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just like...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.56,0:16:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,a child telling his parents all the fun things\Nthat happened at school today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.14,0:16:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That was how he talked to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.37,0:16:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The story of the world coming to an end, my ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.54,0:16:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just some nonsense this crazy kid was spouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.41,0:16:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I thought at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.78,0:16:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it an interesting story?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.85,0:16:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you enjoy listening, Mr. Martin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's talk about you next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.77,0:16:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been working for The Baby for three years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.64,0:16:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you investigate me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.97,0:17:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You were in prison before that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Those eight years must have been tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.81,0:17:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You were a model inmate, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.68,0:17:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You were able to get out of the place,\Neven though you committed murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.72,0:17:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Living with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.55,0:17:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman you killed, I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.72,0:17:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name was Edda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.06,0:17:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure have poor taste, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.96,0:17:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She was a terrible drug addict.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You tried your best to get her off the drugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.33,0:17:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not something that's easy to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it love?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:35.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to get hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.34,0:17:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,She got back on her feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.44,0:17:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She cooked dinner and waited for you to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.48,0:17:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A happy life started.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.71,0:17:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm asking if you want to get beat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But on that night...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you saw a terrible sight when\Nyou returned to your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Her old boyfriend was in the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She was doing drugs again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,She looked at you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and mumbled something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She kept repeating to herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.84,0:18:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.44,0:18:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.71,0:18:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But you shot and killed her, along with the man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.72,0:18:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what was determined at the trial, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.65,0:18:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She killed herself, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.99,0:18:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Your attorney found gunpowder on her hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so he deduced that she committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you still confessed to killing her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,She begged you to kill her, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.25,0:18:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the one who shot her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.55,0:18:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She asked you, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,To shoot her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.69,0:19:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.86,0:19:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,kill me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Martin!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.85,0:19:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She shot herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.65,0:19:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.16,0:19:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me, right? Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.94,0:19:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing! I was right, wasn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.81,0:19:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You deserted her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you made her desire come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:19:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.08,0:19:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.86,0:20:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She froze to death when you were ten, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You deserted your mother back then, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.06,0:20:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I was right again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.13,0:20:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised I was actually right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:24.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You carried your alcoholic mother home\Non your back every day, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And your mother kept telling you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to leave her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, you still carried your mother back every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.05,0:20:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that night...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't sleep in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.06,0:20:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You left her there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.42,0:21:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You left your mother there, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The next morning, you were told...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that your mother froze to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But at the time, you thought to yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,that it wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.83,0:21:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You only left her there because she asked you to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.04,0:21:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Both your mother and your drug-addicted\Ngirlfriend wanted to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.44,0:21:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You only let those who wanted to die, die.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.91,0:21:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You aren't wrong. You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.88,0:21:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You set them free from the misery of living.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva wants to die, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.01,0:22:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just then, the devil arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.61,0:22:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I passed by, making sure not to look at the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.62,0:22:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't look...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.29,0:22:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't look...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.82,0:22:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I must not look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I recited that to myself, like a child.
